                    <ul>
                        <li ng-repeat="phone in phones">
                            <span>{{phone.name}}</span>
                            <p>{{phone.snippet}}</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="menu">
                        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/experience-bar">Experience Bar</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/experience-gallery">Experience Galley</a></li>
                    </ul>


                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-8" style="background-color:green;height:100px">
                    Mission
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ut odio molestie, vulputate est a, rutrum nunc. Nunc mollis nisl eget mauris ultricies commodo. Nam blandit libero ut urna pellentesque vehicula.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4" style="background-color:lightgray;height:100px;">Meet creator <br> Michael Chen</div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12" style="background-color:lightcyan;">.col-sm-12</div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-7" style="background-color:lightcyan;">.col-sm-12</div>
                <div class="col-sm-5" style="background-color:lightcyan;">.col-sm-12</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4" style="background-color:lavenderblush;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12" style="background-color:orange;">
                    Updates from creator
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ut odio molestie, vulputate est a, rutrum nunc. Nunc mollis                    nisl eget mauris ultricies commodo. Nam blandit libero ut urna pellentesque vehicula.
                    </p>
                </div>
